WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.350
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:05.110
doing? This will probably be one of the

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:08.110
most important messages I've ever given

00:00:08.120 --> 00:00:11.150
on this platform, so I really want

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.070
you to listen carefully. I'm

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.110
going to start it out like this:

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.790
my wife and I

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:21.029
gave you the list of the readout

00:00:21.039 --> 00:00:24.429
of that visitation from that man.

00:00:24.439 --> 00:00:26.230
I've tried to find him; I don't know

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:29.429
if he's still alive or if he went on

00:00:29.439 --> 00:00:32.229
to go home with the Lord, but

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:35.229
he had another visitation

00:00:35.239 --> 00:00:38.350
back in 2014,

00:00:38.360 --> 00:00:42.229
the same year that I had

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:44.270
mine. He went to

00:00:44.270 --> 00:00:44.280
the

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:48.430
tribulation, and the Lord showed him

00:00:48.430 --> 00:00:48.440
the

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:52.310
tribulation. Every single thing that

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.310
he

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:56.790
saw was different than what

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:59.630
the Lord showed me, which is absolutely

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:00.990
amazing,

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:03.310
but they fit together like a puzzle.

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:06.310
I'm going to have my wife read

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:08.870
his visitation; it's a dream he had.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:12.910
Now, I believe I had an

00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:12.920
out-of-body

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:15.350
experience. I

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:16.630
haven't been able to speak to

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.870
this man, but I'm going to tell you all,

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:21.749
it's like you can take a puzzle piece from

00:01:21.749 --> 00:01:21.759
someone

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:23.390
who had the other

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.550
pieces and

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.990
put them

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.310
together to make a whole puzzle. I know

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:31.429
there's probably someone out there that has

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:33.550
more pieces to the puzzle, even

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:35.590
about the asteroid. I told you all about

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:38.109
the asteroid hitting Miami

00:01:38.119 --> 00:01:40.749
in the Atlantic Ocean,

00:01:40.759 --> 00:01:43.870
wiping out the islands, and

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:46.109
the water coming inland

00:01:46.119 --> 00:01:48.789
into the East Coast. Whenever I told

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:52.429
you the Lord said,

00:01:52.429 --> 00:01:52.439
'Woe,

00:01:52.439 --> 00:01:55.350
America! Woe, America! I have favored you

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:58.670
and I have loved you above all nations,

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:00.469
and I have prospered you

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:02.990
above all nations,'I gave that

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.630
word and put it down. It was

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:06.429
just a couple of months ago. It's almost

00:02:06.439 --> 00:02:08.510
like the Lord didn't

00:02:08.510 --> 00:02:08.520
want me

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:11.190
to find this word until now

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.790
because it would have

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:15.309
influenced my word. Am I

00:02:15.319 --> 00:02:16.830
hearing this, or am I hearing the word

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:19.350
from this man? That's why this has just

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:22.630
been so divine,

00:02:22.630 --> 00:02:22.640
though;

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:25.430
it's just like a clock, it's

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:28.270
perfect. Finding it right

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:31.910
now just shook me, y'all, because

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:33.710
whenever I hear the Lord, I'm telling you,

00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:36.270
I hear the Lord. And whenever I tell

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:38.509
you I have a visitation from the Lord

00:02:38.519 --> 00:02:40.710
Jesus and I see him face to face, there's

00:02:40.720 --> 00:02:43.309
nothing that I've ever exaggerated.

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:46.790
I speak exactly what he says to tell

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.949
you all. That's why it shook me so

00:02:48.949 --> 00:02:48.959
much—this

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:51.430
visitation from this man having

00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:53.790
similarities, even things

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:58.110
about the boat and

00:02:58.110 --> 00:02:58.120
the

00:02:58.120 --> 00:03:00.030
EMP and everything.

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:03.670
He's seen it all. He even said that

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:05.789
you'll hear about the earthquake

00:03:05.799 --> 00:03:07.030
that I told you all was going to

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:10.750
happen in Portland, Oregon. He saw it, and

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:13.110
it's amazing the detail that he

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:14.589
brings. You

00:03:14.589 --> 00:03:14.599
can

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:16.430
go back and listen to

00:03:16.440 --> 00:03:18.630
some of my videos of what the Lord spoke

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:20.949
to me. He'll even say

00:03:20.959 --> 00:03:22.350
in this that he doesn't know if

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:25.229
this is pre-trib or during the

00:03:25.239 --> 00:03:28.949
tribulation,

00:03:28.949 --> 00:03:28.959
and

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:31.190
I

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:34.309
don't either. All I know is I saw

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:36.630
this stuff. I don't know a timeframe,

00:03:36.630 --> 00:03:36.640
but

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:39.670
I know that it is a

00:03:39.670 --> 00:03:39.680
spanking—it's

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:43.149
a judgment and a

00:03:43.149 --> 00:03:43.159
wake-up.

00:03:43.159 --> 00:03:45.429
I personally believe we're still

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:48.509
here for some of this. So

00:03:48.519 --> 00:03:50.429
I'm going to link my

00:03:50.439 --> 00:03:53.470
videos in the description

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:54.789
so you all can find

00:03:54.799 --> 00:03:57.390
them easily—the words that I've given

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.229
that

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:01.390
go just like a mirror to what

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:03.509
this man saw. I don't

00:04:03.519 --> 00:04:05.390
even know how old this man is, but he was

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:09.830
a professor at ORU. My wife was at

00:04:09.830 --> 00:04:09.840
ORU

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.630
going to school

00:04:11.640 --> 00:04:13.670
there; she never knew him as a professor,

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:16.390
but

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:17.629
I don't know if he's

00:04:17.629 --> 00:04:17.639
gone

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:19.310
home to be with the Lord.

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:23.550
We're going to go straight to my

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:26.189
wife, and she's going to read this

00:04:26.199 --> 00:04:28.469
visitation. Please listen to the whole

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:32.230
thing; it's very serious. Hi family. I

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:33.710
just want to take a minute and say thank

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:36.870
you so much for all the encouragement

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:39.469
from the last time I read. I take

00:04:39.479 --> 00:04:41.830
reading things from

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.830
the Lord very seriously and really wanted to do

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:46.270
honor to God through it.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:51.390
I will just start

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:54.790
this. This week I had a dream. It was a

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:58.510
terribly frightening dream. In it, I saw a

00:04:58.520 --> 00:05:01.510
huge angel standing suspended in the air

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:02.950
over New York

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:05.870
Harbor. It looked so large that it

00:05:05.880 --> 00:05:09.230
covered the night sky. His body was clad

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:12.350
in golden armor as if he was going to

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:15.870
war. His face and entire being were so

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:18.150
bright that I could not gaze up at him

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:21.510
for long. White beams of light seemed to

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:23.670
radiate outward from him in all

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:26.070
directions. He was standing over the

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:29.189
Statue of Liberty. It was night, but I

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.270
could hardly see the lights around him

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:34.029
coming from New York City as he blazed

00:05:34.039 --> 00:05:37.510
so brightly with divine light. He reached

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:40.350
for his belt that was covered with a red

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:42.830
sash around his midsection and drew out

00:05:42.840 --> 00:05:46.469
his sword. It was so massive it blazed

00:05:46.479 --> 00:05:49.230
with light and fire all around it. It

00:05:49.240 --> 00:05:53.550
looked at least 100 feet long. I have never

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:56.150
felt such fear when I saw an angel

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:59.110
before. I just knew this mighty

00:05:59.110 --> 00:05:59.120
warring

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:01.510
spirit had authority from the very

00:06:01.520 --> 00:06:04.870
throne of God. He had a grim expression

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:06.990
as he held this mighty sword over his

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:09.710
head with both hands. I could see that he

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.029
was poised to hit the Statue of Liberty

00:06:12.039 --> 00:06:14.909
and cleave it in two. I trembled and

00:06:14.919 --> 00:06:17.270
tried to hide, but the angel was looking

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:19.710
directly at me and I knew there was

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:23.589
nowhere to go that he would not see me.

00:06:23.599 --> 00:06:27.550
Then he spoke. His voice was like thunder

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:30.029
and echoed throughout the whole harbor.

00:06:30.039 --> 00:06:33.469
He said, 'How long will you refuse to

00:06:33.479 --> 00:06:35.390
humble yourself,

00:06:35.390 --> 00:06:35.400
O

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:37.990
America? You have been weighed in the

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:41.629
balances of God and found wanting. Your

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:44.350
beginning was great and noble, but your

00:06:44.360 --> 00:06:47.070
end shall be disgrace and

00:06:47.070 --> 00:06:47.080
destruction.'Okay,

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:49.710
hold on right here. Did you hear

00:06:49.720 --> 00:06:53.189
that? Again, read that again: 'How long

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:55.390
will you refuse to humble yourself,

00:06:55.390 --> 00:06:55.400
O

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:57.790
America? You have been weighed in the

00:06:57.800 --> 00:07:00.869
balances of God and found wanting. Your

00:07:00.879 --> 00:07:03.589
beginning was great and noble, but your

00:07:03.599 --> 00:07:06.230
end shall be disgrace and

00:07:06.230 --> 00:07:06.240
destruction.'That's

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:08.909
exactly the word the Lord gave me,

00:07:08.909 --> 00:07:08.919
which

00:07:08.919 --> 00:07:12.270
my son can vouch for. It's to the

00:07:12.270 --> 00:07:12.280
T,

00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:15.830
y'all. It was identical.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:18.230
There's no word missing from what

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.390
the Lord gave me.

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.710
'But I have weighed you in the

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:23.869
balance and you are

00:07:23.869 --> 00:07:23.879
lacking.'He

00:07:23.879 --> 00:07:25.790
kept saying this

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.230
to me three times.

00:07:30.599 --> 00:07:32.790
He was quoting Daniel to

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:35.430
me. Thus saith the Lord of Heaven's

00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:39.029
armies, the Lord of hosts: 'Time is running

00:07:39.039 --> 00:07:42.309
out. The bowls of my wrath are full of my

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:46.189
fury and judgment. They shall be poured

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:49.629
out upon you. You shall drink them down

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:53.510
to the dregs, every drop. I have come to

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.869
you day and night pleading with you to

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:59.510
return to me for over 100 years. I am

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:02.550
merciful and longsuffering. It brings me

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:05.350
no joy to judge you, but you have

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:07.990
hardened your hearts and scoffed at my

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.589
warnings through my prophets and my holy

00:08:10.599 --> 00:08:13.230
servants. I brought you from nothing and

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:16.029
exalted you, O America, higher than any

00:08:16.039 --> 00:08:19.149
other nation, but now you have fallen

00:08:19.159 --> 00:08:21.909
lower than Sodom. You have sinned greater

00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:24.710
than Egypt. You have become prouder than

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:27.510
Babylon and Persia. You have become more

00:08:27.520 --> 00:08:30.350
selfish than Rome. You have exalted

00:08:30.360 --> 00:08:32.990
yourself in your own wisdom higher than

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:36.149
Greece. You have more idols and high

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:38.630
places of idolatry and luxury than any

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:41.230
Gentile kingdom in history. Your

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:44.230
beginning was pure and great, but now the

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:46.670
stench of your sin and filth fills my

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:49.230
nostrils. I shall cut you in pieces, and

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:51.310
you shall reap the harvest of wrath from

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:54.070
what you have sown. You shall no longer

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:56.949
be the queen of nations. Now you shall

00:08:56.959 --> 00:08:59.030
bear your shame and become the lowest of

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:02.509
the heathen nations. Now, as Agag, you

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:05.910
shall be hacked in pieces.

00:09:05.910 --> 00:09:05.920
O

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:09.790
earth, earth, earth, hear ye the word of

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:13.269
the Lord!'Then to my horror, that massive

00:09:13.279 --> 00:09:16.350
sword came smashing down on Lady Liberty.

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:18.590
When it hit the top of her head, there

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:21.509
was a blinding flash of light and that

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:23.870
sword split her in two right down the

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:26.870
middle. Then the sword came again and

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:29.230
again against her. It divided her in

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:31.790
pieces, and as the sword would finish each

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:35.350
strike, fires would burst forth. I heard

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:38.069
terrible explosions. The vision of the

00:09:38.079 --> 00:09:41.389
statue ended with an earthquake as it

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:44.150
was hacked into pieces and sunk into the

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:47.069
harbor. I was weeping and crying out to

00:09:47.079 --> 00:09:49.829
God for mercy. Never had I seen this side

00:09:49.839 --> 00:09:52.750
of God before.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:55.110
Never had I

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.590
seen the wrath of the

00:09:57.600 --> 00:10:00.590
Almighty. Then

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:03.949
the dream shifted

00:10:03.959 --> 00:10:06.069
and I started to zoom outward from New

00:10:06.079 --> 00:10:08.870
York Harbor, traveling in the

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:10.150
air over

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:13.389
America. What I saw was horror beyond

00:10:13.399 --> 00:10:15.350
anything I have ever

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:19.350
seen. I saw the United States seem to

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.910
crack in two with a giant earthquake

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:23.949
right down the middle. I saw the

00:10:23.959 --> 00:10:26.110
southeastern United States covered with

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:29.509
a giant wave of water from the ocean. I

00:10:29.519 --> 00:10:31.910
saw a massive earthquake that just

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:34.150
seemed to crack off the coast of

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:37.150
California. It reminded me of a

00:10:37.150 --> 00:10:37.160
saltine

00:10:37.160 --> 00:10:40.350
cracker that just cracked, and the great

00:10:40.360 --> 00:10:43.030
cities along the West Coast just fell

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:45.949
into the ocean all the way from Mexico

00:10:45.959 --> 00:10:48.870
up to Alaska, and giant waves flooded

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:51.350
inland until much of the West Coast just

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:54.030
wasn't there. It disappeared into the

00:10:54.040 --> 00:10:56.590
Pacific Ocean. Do you all remember that

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:59.790
word? That's exactly what I saw. Then

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:02.550
I saw three giant rocket missiles that

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:05.389
took off into the air. Two came from

00:11:05.399 --> 00:11:07.629
the ocean waters and one came from

00:11:07.639 --> 00:11:10.430
land. All

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:13.350
of them blew up in the air

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:15.910
in the upper atmosphere within five

00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:15.920
seconds

00:11:15.920 --> 00:11:18.430
of each other.

00:11:18.440 --> 00:11:22.350
They were terrible nuclear bombs,

00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:24.670
but the last one was the biggest and it

00:11:24.680 --> 00:11:26.910
created a huge mushroom cloud over the

00:11:26.920 --> 00:11:30.230
Midwest part of America. Then the ground

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:33.069
shook and everything went

00:11:33.079 --> 00:11:36.110
black. There wasn't any electric light

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:38.750
coming out of any of the homes. Then

00:11:38.760 --> 00:11:41.269
candles began to be lit and a

00:11:41.279 --> 00:11:44.230
little light was seen. There were other

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:46.790
nuclear explosions and many people

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:49.509
perished throughout the nation. There was

00:11:49.519 --> 00:11:52.190
just twisted metal and charred debris in

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:55.269
cities that once were tall and majestic.

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:58.030
There was widespread looting and gangs

00:11:58.040 --> 00:12:00.269
roaming about everywhere with guns,

00:12:00.279 --> 00:12:02.389
stealing whatever food and supplies they

00:12:02.399 --> 00:12:05.470
could find. Then I saw what looked like

00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:08.509
elite riot police go

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:11.389
into communities and cities,

00:12:11.389 --> 00:12:11.399
force

00:12:11.399 --> 00:12:13.189
the people out of their homes, and bring

00:12:13.189 --> 00:12:13.199
them

00:12:13.199 --> 00:12:14.670
into what looked like

00:12:14.680 --> 00:12:17.910
concentration camps. Some of

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:21.069
these police armies had light

00:12:21.079 --> 00:12:24.590
blue helmets on. Hundreds of thousands of

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:27.629
people were arrested in this way. Many

00:12:27.639 --> 00:12:29.949
would not cooperate and were just shot

00:12:29.959 --> 00:12:31.550
and left dead in their

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:35.110
homes. But there were millions of hidden

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:37.389
groups that escaped the first wave of

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:39.310
these

