00:30:43.240 --> 00:30:47.070
The wages of sin is death.

00:30:47.080 --> 00:30:50.789
It's time today to ask

00:30:50.799 --> 00:30:52.669
Jesus to be your Lord and

00:30:52.679 --> 00:30:55.789
Savior.

00:31:06.679 --> 00:31:08.750
Are you ready to stand at that great

00:31:08.760 --> 00:31:10.909
white throne of judgment?

00:31:10.919 --> 00:31:12.950
When

00:31:12.960 --> 00:31:14.389
he says, 'What

00:31:14.399 --> 00:31:17.230
did you do for

00:31:24.200 --> 00:31:27.830
me?'will

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:35.230
your

00:31:35.240 --> 00:31:37.789
cup be empty?

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:47.430
I pray God has mercy.

00:31:50.159 --> 00:31:52.350
We're running out of time.

00:31:52.360 --> 00:31:55.310
I always look for

00:31:55.320 --> 00:31:58.389
him during the September timeframe, during

00:31:58.389 --> 00:31:58.399
Rosh Hashanah.

00:31:58.399 --> 00:32:02.710
Could it be this year?

00:32:10.039 --> 00:32:12.470
I've rambled on long enough,

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:14.909
but I wanted you to

00:32:14.919 --> 00:32:17.590
see the parallels.

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:24.990
God is speaking to different prophetic

00:32:25.000 --> 00:32:26.310
voices to

00:32:26.320 --> 00:32:28.710
warn them.

00:32:30.559 --> 00:32:33.629
He

00:32:33.639 --> 00:32:36.149
put us to be a watchman on the wall. I

00:32:36.159 --> 00:32:39.350
feel like I'm Paul Revere riding my horse

00:32:39.360 --> 00:32:41.190
through the towns telling

00:32:41.200 --> 00:32:43.750
the minutemen, 'Jesus is coming! Jesus

00:32:50.200 --> 00:32:52.430
is

00:32:52.430 --> 00:32:52.440
coming!'to

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:55.029
get you woke up for the spiritual war.

00:33:19.279 --> 00:33:22.190
Father, I thank you for

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:24.990
every single person.

00:33:31.760 --> 00:33:34.830
Say, 'Jesus,

00:33:34.840 --> 00:33:38.110
come into my heart. Write my name in the

00:33:38.120 --> 00:33:42.629
Lamb's Book of Life. I

00:33:42.639 --> 00:33:45.430
make you my Lord and personal

00:34:05.190 --> 00:34:05.200
Savior.'He

00:34:22.879 --> 00:34:25.310
made it so a little

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:28.829
child can get saved;

00:34:33.240 --> 00:34:37.430
it's easy.

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:38.950
Father, I

00:34:38.960 --> 00:34:40.270
thank you

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:42.589
for

00:34:42.599 --> 00:34:44.349
healings and wholeness in

00:34:44.359 --> 00:34:46.710
these people's homes. We call in unsaved loved ones in Jesus'name. Angels, go out and bring them home. We're running out of time. Our children, wayward husbands, moms, and dads—we call them home in Jesus'name. We thank you that you don't want one to perish. We bind the demonic distractions

00:34:46.710 --> 00:34:46.720
and spirits that would hold them down and command you to release our

00:34:46.720 --> 00:34:48.710
loved ones. We call

00:35:59.400 --> 00:36:02.150
the harvest of

00:36:02.160 --> 00:36:04.870
souls in the name of Jesus. Father,

00:36:04.880 --> 00:36:07.550
give us creative

00:36:07.550 --> 00:36:07.560
ideas

00:36:07.560 --> 00:36:10.829
to bring souls into your kingdom.

00:36:13.280 --> 00:36:15.589
I thank you

00:36:22.200 --> 00:36:23.630
for the anointing of

00:36:23.640 --> 00:36:26.069
the Holy Ghost to flow through us.

00:36:36.040 --> 00:36:38.589
It's time for a great

00:36:38.599 --> 00:36:40.990
new outpouring of your spirit—new wine and new

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:46.510
wineskins.

00:36:49.160 --> 00:36:51.270
Fan the flame in

00:36:51.280 --> 00:36:54.069
these people today in Jesus'name. We call

00:36:54.069 --> 00:36:54.079
for

00:36:54.079 --> 00:36:57.230
a fullness of fire,

00:36:57.240 --> 00:36:59.630
like gasoline on a

00:37:01.079 --> 00:37:04.349
flame.

00:37:05.390 --> 00:37:05.400
I

00:37:08.319 --> 00:37:11.630
want to tell

00:37:11.640 --> 00:37:13.470
you all thank you for watching.

00:37:21.079 --> 00:37:22.390
If you could click the

00:37:22.400 --> 00:37:24.829
notification bell, it really would bless

00:37:24.839 --> 00:37:28.630
us. If you could like the video and put a

00:37:28.640 --> 00:37:30.910
comment down below,

00:37:30.920 --> 00:37:33.790
we're curious

00:37:33.800 --> 00:37:35.430
where your heart's at.

00:37:37.640 --> 00:37:40.470
We thank you

00:37:40.480 --> 00:37:42.750
all for your support.

00:37:58.800 --> 00:38:01.990
You're helping get the gospel

00:38:02.000 --> 00:38:03.589
spread throughout the world. Another

00:38:03.599 --> 00:38:05.430
person gave their heart to Jesus

00:38:05.430 --> 00:38:05.440
and

00:38:05.440 --> 00:38:07.950
some got baptized in

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:10.589
the Holy Ghost this week.

00:38:17.480 --> 00:38:19.950
Thank you for all your

00:38:19.960 --> 00:38:22.069
love and kindness. God bless

00:38:22.079 --> 00:38:24.510
you all;

00:38:24.520 --> 00:38:27.270
Jesus

00:38:27.270 --> 00:38:27.280
loves

00:38:27.280 --> 00:38:30.990
you so much. We will

00:38:31.000 --> 00:38:33.510
see you next time. Y'all have a blessed

00:38:33.520 --> 00:38:36.990
and wonderful day. Bye-bye.

